txt.en: 'Meow! Goodness, you are up to Book V of the Epic quest series. That is a very good series of quests, if you ask me. All those bits with Skorgr√≠m and the Dourhands, and then you end with a Dragon. Terribly exciting!\n\nOh well, you'll be able to skip all that once you complete this quest.
'Here we go! When you complete this quest you'll be flagged as having completed Book V of the Epic.'
Level Up: Volume II: Book V
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book V of the Epic quest series of volume II.
